- Avoid pointless warnings (Matthias Clasen)
- Honour the SmRestartNever SmRestartStyleHint (Caolan McNamara)
- Default clients to RESTART_IF_RUNNING instead of NEVER (Caolan McNamara)
- Code cleanups (Vincent)

