	* Marcel Telka (sk)

===============
Version 2.21.93
===============

Misc

	* Remove hard dependency on esound, this is handled by
	  mate-settings-daemon now (Bastien Nocera)

Session Manager

	* Don't start the sound server, and play the login sound when
	  mate-settings-daemon tells us the sound server has started (Bastien
	  Nocera)

